        <p rend="left Azbuka2" id="715e5f0d-4d15-4887-9310-5224f066665b"><choice><reg>Был</reg></choice>у дурака<choice><reg>нож</reg></choice><choice><reg>очен</reg></choice><choice><reg>хорош</reg></choice>.<choice><reg>Стал</reg></choice><choice><reg>дурак</reg></choice><choice><reg>этим</reg></choice><choice><reg>ножем</reg></choice>гвоздь<choice><reg>резать</reg></choice>.<choice><reg>Нож</reg></choice>гвоздя не<choice><reg>резал</reg></choice>. Тогда<choice><reg>дурак</reg></choice><choice><reg>сказал</reg></choice>:<choice><reg>дурен</reg></choice>мой<choice><reg>нож</reg></choice>. И<choice><reg>стал</reg></choice><choice><reg>этим</reg></choice><choice><reg>ножем</reg></choice><choice><reg>жидкий</reg></choice></p>
